{"first_name":"Yovav (Jay)","last_name":"Meydad","permalink":"jay-meydad","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/person/jay-meydad","homepage_url":"http://www.meydad.com","birthplace":"Israel","twitter_username":"jaym","blog_url":"http://www.meydad.com","blog_feed_url":"http://www.meydad.com/feed/","affiliation_name":"Spark Networks","born_year":null,"born_month":null,"born_day":null,"tag_list":"vp-product, snap, snap-shots, product-management","alias_list":null,"created_at":"Thu Feb 21 01:32:24 UTC 2008","updated_at":"Sun Jan 22 09:48:31 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>Yovav (Jay) Meydad is the co-founder and CEO of Hitpad. Hitpad for iPad provides a quick and way to stay current and see what&#8217;s going on today. The product was launched at Techonomy3 event in Tel Aviv on April 2011.</p>\n\n<p>Prior to founding Hitpad with Nir Holtzman Ninio (company&#8217;s CTO), Jay spent 4 years as the Vice President of Products &amp; Operations at Snap Technologies, a distributed media company with a 20% U.S. reach which offers services in content distribution (Snap Shots) &amp; contextual advertising (Snap LinkAds).</p>\n\n<p>Prior to Snap, Jay served 3 years as the VP of Product &amp; Project Management for Spark Networks, a leading online personals service provider. While at Spark, he oversaw the product and design teams, and was responsible for the execution of multiple product and feature launches across a large network of web properties including JDate.com and AmericanSingles.com. </p>\n\n<p>Prior to Spark Networks, Jay worked as Director of Account Management for ICQ Mobile, an AOL company, where he oversaw ICQ&#8217;s relationships with wireless service providers worldwide, including Vodafone, O2 and Rogers AT&amp;T Wireless. </p>\n\n<p>Before ICQ, Jay served in various product development &amp; management roles at a variety of technology companies. </p>\n\n<p>Jay earned a Bachelor of Science degree in Information Systems Engineering from the Ben Gurion University, Israel.</p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,99],"assets/images/resized/0002/5645/25645v2-max-150x150.jpg"],[[250,166],"assets/images/resized/0002/5645/25645v2-max-250x250.jpg"],[[450,299],"assets/images/resized/0002/5645/25645v2-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":""},"degrees":[{"degree_type":"B.Sc.","subject":"Information Systems Engineering","institution":"Ben Gurion University of the Negev","graduated_year":null,"graduated_month":null,"graduated_day":null}],"relationships":[{"is_past":false,"title":"Co-Founder & CEO","firm":{"name":"Hitpad","permalink":"hitpad","type_of_entity":"company","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,36],"assets/images/resized/0012/9630/129630v2-max-150x150.png"],[[200,49],"assets/images/resized/0012/9630/129630v2-max-250x250.png"],[[200,49],"assets/images/resized/0012/9630/129630v2-max-450x450.png"]],"attribution":null}}},{"is_past":false,"title":"Co-Founder, CEO","firm":{"name":"Pixplit","permalink":"pixplit","type_of_entity":"company","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,39],"assets/images/resized/0020/3436/203436v3-max-150x150.jpg"],[[234,62],"assets/images/resized/0020/3436/203436v3-max-250x250.jpg"],[[234,62],"assets/images/resized/0020/3436/203436v3-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":null}}},{"is_past":false,"title":"","firm":{"name":"Pixplit","permalink":"pixplit","type_of_entity":"company","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,39],"assets/images/resized/0020/3436/203436v3-max-150x150.jpg"],[[234,62],"assets/images/resized/0020/3436/203436v3-max-250x250.jpg"],[[234,62],"assets/images/resized/0020/3436/203436v3-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":null}}},{"is_past":true,"title":"Vice President, Products & Operations","firm":{"name":"Snap Technologies","permalink":"snap-technologies","type_of_entity":"company","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,50],"assets/images/resized/0001/2139/12139v1-max-150x150.png"],[[216,73],"assets/images/resized/0001/2139/12139v1-max-250x250.png"],[[216,73],"assets/images/resized/0001/2139/12139v1-max-450x450.png"]],"attribu